ch%20ingredient%20while%20reducing%20portion%20sizes%20if%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20toppings%20to%20make%20sure%20everything%20fits%20in%20the%20bowl%20or%20burrito.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20generally%2C%20across%20the%20board%2C%20we're%20always%20more%20accurate%20than%20a%20comparable%20person%20running%20at%20the%20same%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20Fukuba%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20more%20consistent%20and%20accurate%20than%20a%20person%20normally%20would%20be%20going%20at%20the%20same%20speed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Chipotle%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20story%20but%20pointed%20to%20CEO%20Brian%20Niccol's%20comments%20in%20an%20earnings%20call%20on%20Wednesday%20referencing%20Hyphen%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-hiring-a-robot-to-do-a-task-employees-hate-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAutocado%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20robot%20that%20helps%20cut%20prep%20time%20for%20Chipotle's%20guacamole%20in%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20excited%20about%20each%20of%20these%20initiatives%2C%20and%20I%20strongly%20believe%20we%20will%20see%20some%20impactful%20back-of-house%20changes%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come%20that%20will%20help%20to%20improve%20consistency%20in%20our%20restaurants%20and%20drive%20a%20better%20overall%20experience%20for%20our%20teams%20and%20our%20guests%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7371117-ee03-4fd2-accc-a45db88961b9%5C%22%3EThe%20'secret%20sauce'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20replacing%20frontline%20human%20employees%20with%20robots%20takes%20away%20from%20a%20key%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftypical-chipotle-customer-demographic-white-married-millennial-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomer%3C%2Fa%3E%20experience%20that%20Chipotle%20employees%20have%20delivered%2C%20perhaps%20almost%20by%20accident%2C%20over%20the%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20involves%20being%20able%20