%22%3E%3Cem%3ESFGate%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20hikers%20need%20to%20get%20permits%20ahead%20of%20time%20for%20the%20challenging%2014-16-mile%20round-trip%20hike%20to%20Half%20Dome.%20Recalling%20the%20incident%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20outlet%2C%20her%20father%20said%20that%20she%20was%20very%20happy%20and%20told%20him%20that%20she%20loved%20him.%20%26quot%3BShe%20told%20me%20it%20was%20something%20that%20was%20on%20her%20bucket%20list%20that%20she%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20and%20she%20was%20so%20happy%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20had%20hiked%20together%20for%20%26quot%3Bthousands%20of%20miles%26quot%3B%20at%20that%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20way%2010%20minutes%20before%2C%20when%20she%20was%20up%20there%20smiling%20ear%20to%20ear%2C%20that%20I%20thought%20I%20only%20had%2010%20minutes%20left%20with%20her.%20It%20was%20a%20tragedy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%C2%A0Rohloff%20told%20SFGate%20that%20they%20heard%20a%20%26quot%3Bloud%20thunderclap%26quot%3B%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20arrived%20at%20the%20summit%20and%20realised%20they%20had%20to%20start%20descending%20right%20away.%20%26quot%3BA%20black%20cloud%20was%20rolling%20in%20like%20gangbusters.%20I%20said%3A%20'We%20have%20to%20get%20down%20now%2C%20because%20we%20can't%20be%20up%20here%20with%20any%20rain.%20It%20rolled%20in%20literally%20out%20of%20nowhere%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrace%20informed%20him%20that%20her%20new%20hiking%20shoes%20were%20not%20providing%20enough%20traction%20on%20the%20route%20as%20they%20descended.%20%26quot%3BDad%2C%20my%20shoes%20are%20so%20slippery%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rohloff%20recalled%20her%20saying.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20calm%20her%20down%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOK%2C%20let's%20do%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20before%20he%20realised%20what%20was%20going%20on%2C%20