20in%20the%20home%20gym%2C%20Felix%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20Allyson%20Felix%20reigned%20supreme%20in%20track%20and%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinning%20her%20first%20World%20Championship%20gold%20as%20a%2019-year-old%20phenom%20in%202005%2C%20she%20went%20on%20to%20earn%2011%20Olympic%20medals%20(seven%20of%20them%20gold)%20and%20a%20record-setting%2020%20World%20Championship%20medals%20in%20all.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20retired%20after%20the%202022%20season%2C%20Felix%20had%20secured%20her%20title%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20decorated%20American%20athletes%20in%20sports%20history%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2038%2C%20Felix%20told%20Business%20Insider%20how%20she%20maintained%20peak%20performance%20and%20dealt%20with%20the%20intense%20pressure%20of%20elite%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20full-time%20commitment%2C%20full-time%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Olympics%20can%20be%20kind%20of%20crazy%20because%20for%20us%2C%20it's%20about%2021%20seconds%20that%20you%20get%20to%20show%20the%20world%20what%20you've%20been%20working%20on%20for%20four%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFelix%2C%20a%20vocal%20advocate%20for%20working%20parents%2C%20spoke%20to%20BI%20in%20an%20interview%20about%20her%20partnership%20with%20Pampers%20in%20support%20of%20premature%20babies%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20her%20competitive%20peak%2C%20she%20trained%20for%20five%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20to%20develop%20the%20precise%20technique%20needed%20to%20excel%20at%20sprinting.%20But%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20a%20full-time%20athlete%20to%20get%20faster%2C%20become%20more%20efficient%20at%20running%2C%20or%20boost%20your%20recovery%20like%20an%20Olympian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFelix%20shared%20three%20lessons%20from%20her%20Olympic%20career%20that%20can%20help%20everyday%20athletes%20level%20up%20on%20their%20next%20run%20or%20workout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b04eba2-f4a2-44c1-8532-4b7907e15db8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERest%20days%20are%20crucial%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%2017-year%20elite%20athletic%20career%2C%20Felix%20dominated%20the%20200-meter%20sprint%20and%20helped%20the%20US%20women's%20relay%20team%20lock%20in%20multiple%20gold%20medals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20taking%20time%20to%20rest%20was%20crucial%20to%20staying%20fast%20enough%20to%20compete%20at%20the%20top%20of%20her%20game%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecovery%20was%20huge.%20It%20was%20a%20huge%20lesson%20that%20I%20had%20to%20learn.%20My%20coach%20always%20said%20a%20day%20off%20is%20just%20as%20important%20as%20the%20days%20that%20we%20really%20get%20after%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Felix%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20can%20be%20tempting%20to%20work%20out%20every%20day%20to%20make%20faster%20progress%2C%20skipping%20rest%20days%20can%20backfire%20and%20lead%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarning-signs-exercising-too-much-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eovertraining%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20burnout%2C%20injury%2C%20and%20plateaus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFelix%20also%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factive-recovery-strategies-reduce-muscle-soreness-boost-muscle-gains-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecovery%20strategies%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20foam%20rolling%20and%20massage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20little%20tedious%2C%20not%20fun%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20what%20really%20gave%20me%20such%20longevity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22534c75c9-c35c-42e9-b02c-66961c24495b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarm%20up%20correctly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOlympic%20athletes%20are%20just%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%2C%20they%20feel%20like%20warming%20up%20is%20boring%20and%20want%20to%20get%20right%20to%20the%20good%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20thought%20about%20skipping%20out%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Felix%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20said%20by%20skipping%20a%20warmup%2C%20you'll%20risk%20getting%20hurt%20and%20likely%20worsen%20your%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20competing%2C%20you%20never%20can%20because%20that's%20what%20protects%20you%20from%20injury%2C%26quot%3B%20Felix%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20be%20like%2C%20oh%2C%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20do%20that.%20But%20you%20absolutely%20do%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you're%20healthy%20and%20you%20want%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20it%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20workout%20or%20a%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20warm-up%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20complicated%2C%20either.%20Trainers%20recommend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarm-up-mistakes-do-not-stretch-cardio-before-a-workout-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarm-up%20exercises%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20mirror%20what%20you're%20planning%20to%20do%20for%20your%20main%20session%2C%20such%20as%20drilling%20a%20hip%20hinge%20if%20you're%20deadlifting%20or%20practicing%20some%20bodyweight%20squats%20before%20loading%20up%20a%20barbell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20running%20warm-up%2C%20especially%20if%20you'll%20be%20sprinting%2C%20Felix%20said%20drills%20such%20as%20A%20skips%20and%20B%20skips%20(a%20type%20of%20high-knee%20motion)%20are%20great%20to%20prep%20for%20explosive%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f9e62c1-f837-41e2-94e1-ab57298c1cae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20on%20the%20small%20wins%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20rules%20for%20long-term%20fitness%20success%20is%20to%20just%20keep%20going%2C%20according%20to%20Felix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20you%20only%20achieve%20a%20little%20at%20a%20time%2C%20small%20but%20consistent%20progress%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20see%20lasting%20results%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-workout-weight-loss-plan-legit-running-coach-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20coaches%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20single%20perfect%20workout%20or%20routine%2C%20but%20showing%20up%20consistently%20over%20time%20is%20what%20can%20turn%20your%20goals%20into%20reality%2C%20whether%20you're%20trying%20to%20hit%20your%20personal%20best%20run%20time%20or%20win%20Olympic%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20look%20at%20something%20like%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20or%20competing%20at%20a%20high%20level%2C%20and%20you%20see%20that%20one%20moment%2C%20but%20it's%20just%20like%20in%20anything%20else.%20It%20takes%20the%20dedication%2C%20it%20takes%20all%20of%20the%20little%20moments%20to%20build%20up%20to%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Felix%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20consistently%20putting%20in%20that%20work%20and%20building%20to%20get%20to%20where%20you%20want%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folympic-legend-allyson-felix-tips-to-make-you-better-runner-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721907182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a1574efb2b6bedb05a3d05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folympic-legend-allyson-felix-tips-to-make-you-better-runner-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elite%20sprinter%20Allyson%20Felix%20said%20avoiding%20some%20common%20exercise%20mistakes%20helped%20her%20stay%20at%20the%20top%20of%20her%20game%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22glandsverk%40insider.com%20(Gabby%20Landsverk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folympic-legend-allyson-felix-tips-to-make-you-better-runner-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22V