0Daily%20Telegraph%20that%20their%20client%20was%2019%20and%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bwarned%20against%20speaking%20out%20in%20the%20UK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Federation%20for%20Equestrian%20Sports%20(FEI)%20suspended%20her%20for%20six%20months%2C%20precluding%20her%20from%20competing%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDujardin%20said%20that%20the%20video%20was%20from%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Berror%20in%20judgment%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FcharlottedujardinCBE%2Fposts%2F1015338783283751%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20ashamed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20reignited%20criticism%20of%20equestrian%20sport%20by%20animal-rights%20activists%20who%20say%20that%20the%20Olympics%20should%20be%20for%20human%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20criticism%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20in%202021%2C%20when%20Germany's%20team%20coach%20punched%20a%20horse%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folympic-horse-punch-modern-pentathlon-chaos-athletes-revolt-rule-changes-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20jump%20in%20the%20modern%20pentathlon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20led%20to%20backlash%20from%20animal%20rights%20activists%20and%20ignited%20debate%20on%20horse%20welfare%20and%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Paris%20games%20will%20be%20the%20first%20to%20feature%20an%20official%20dedicated%20to%20the%20welfare%20of%20competition%20horses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202028%20games%20in%20LA%20won't%20feature%20an%20equestrian%20portion%20after%20officials%20voted%20to%20reform%20the%20event.%20(It%20will%20still%20have%20regular%20equestrian%20events%20though.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20animal%20rights%20group%20PETA%20criticized%20Dujardin%20and%20said%20that%20horses%20should%20not%20be%20used%20for%20s