Physics%20question%20be%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20NTA%20had%20decided%20to%20award%20extra%20marks%20to%20a%20select%20group%20of%20students%20who%20had%20marked%20an%20incorrect%20answer%20due%20to%20a%20mistake%20in%20their%20old%20Class%2012%20NCERT%20science%20textbook.%20However%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20only%20one%20correct%20answer%20would%20be%20accepted%2C%20and%20no%20marks%20would%20be%20given%20for%20any%20other%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%20had%20earlier%20pointed%20out%20that%20%26quot%3BQuestion%20No.%2029%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Physics%20section%20had%20two%20correct%20answers%20-%20when%20it%20should%20have%20only%20one%20correct%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20the%20director%20of%20IIT-Delhi%20to%20set%20up%20a%20team%20of%20three%20experts%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20on%20the%20correct%20answer%20for%20a%20particular%20question%20of%20Physics%20by%20the%20next%20day%20noon.%20Based%20on%20the%20findings%20of%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20the%20court%20later%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRegarding%20one%20question%20of%20Physics%20on%20atomic%20theory%2C%20marks%20shall%20not%20be%20given%20for%20two%20options%2C%20but%20only%20for%20one%20answer%2C%20which%20is%20option%20No.%204.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducation%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20had%20earlier%20announced%20that%20the%20final%20results%20for%20the%20medical%20entrance%202024%20NEET-UG%20exam%20will%20be%20declared%20within%20two%20days%20according%20to%20the%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20ruled%20that%20only%20one%20correct%20answer%20from%20a%20set%20of%20four%20answers%20will%20be%20considered%20valid.%20The%20students%20who%20will%20lose%20four%20marks%20include%2044%20who%20had%20scored%20a%20perfect%20720%2F720.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20dismissed%20a%20clutch%20of%20petitions%20seeking%20canc