letely%20new%20stint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHsiao%20was%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20worked%20on%20Microsoft%20Designer%2C%20a%20tool%20that%20helps%20creators%20generate%20graphics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20left%20Microsoft%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%20after%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20and%20said%20his%20career%20progression%20has%20been%20helped%20by%20prioritizing%20growth%20as%20a%20core%20value.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BI%20attribute%20many%20of%20my%20successes%20so%20far%20to%20having%20the%20courage%20to%20grow%20and%20be%20different%20from%20my%20past%20self%2C%26quot%3B%20Hsiao%20said.%20%26quot%3BBe%20different%20if%20you%20want%20different%20results.%20In%20that%20way%2C%20landing%20a%20new%20job%20role%20or%20starting%20a%20new%20business%20ends%20up%20just%20becoming%20a%20side%20effect%20of%20who%20you%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20he%20used%20to%20land%20a%20job%20at%20Microsoft%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221058%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chris%20Hsiao's%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669fbe68fb2b6bedb0598815%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221368%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChris%20Hsiao%20spoke%20about%20his%20experience%20launching%20an%20e-commerce%20startup%20in%20his%20interviews%20with%20Microsoft%3Cp%3EChris%20Hsiao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22920190f7-eba8-4638-b576-adceb1a67efa%5C%22%3EPreparing%20for%20interviews%20at%20Microsoft%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHsiao%20believes%20that%20having%20Facebook%20on%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20helped%20him%20be%20considered%20for%20roles%20at%20other%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20such%20as%20Microsoft.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHe%20said%20hiring%20managers%20look%20for%20prospective%20product%20managers%20who%20can%20talk%20to%20customers%2C%20understand%20what%20they're%20looking%20for%20in%20a%20product%2C%20and%20then%20execute.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20was%20missing%20real-world%20experience%20with%20building%20a%20product%20from%20scratch%20and%20getting%20it%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20consumers%2C%20so%20I%20started%20an%20e-commerce%20business%20with%20my%20girlfriend%20in%20the%20pandemic%20called%20Made%20Space%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHsiao%20spoke%20about%20the%20startup%2C%20which%20designed%20and%20sold%20merchandise%20online%2C%20during%20his%20interviews%20with%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hiring%20process%20at%20Facebook%20and%20Microsoft%20both%20involved%20multiple%20interview%20rounds%20that%20contained%20both%20behavioral%20and%20situational%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kinds%20of%20questions%20that%20came%20up%20included%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20peer%20on%20your%20team%20is%20not%20performing%20well%2C%20what%20would%20you%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20Another%20was%3A%20%26quot%3BCan%20you%20describe%20a%20time%20where%20you%20overcame%20a%20challenge%20and%2C%20if%20you%20had%20three%20teams%20and%20stakeholders%20wanting%20different%20things%2C%20how%20do%20you%20complete%20your%20objective%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20testing%20me%20on%20how%20I%20would%20work%20with%20a%20team%2C%20my%20thinking%20in%20how%20I%20would%20overcome%20challenges%20and%20it%20seemed%20like%20they%20wanted%20to%20know%20how%20I%20would%20handle%20hypothetical%20scenarios%2C%26quot%3B%20Hsiao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22403b9965-b2c3-42e1-a5a2-dfc199affa18%5C%22%3EThree%20priorities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20interview%2C%20he%20would%20practice%20questions%20he%20thought%20would%20come%20up%20after%20creating%20a%20list.%20He%20also%20found%20an%20online%20test%20question%20repository%20that%20gives%20users%20practice%20questions%20and%20answers.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20reps%20%E2%80%94%20I%20did%20that%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20your%20chance%20of%20being