t%20from%20my%20brother%20Captain%20Vikram%20Batra%20to%20Anuj%20Nayyar%20and%20Manoj%20Pandey.%20To%20me%2C%20coming%20here%20is%20like%20doing%20a%20tete-a-tete%20with%20my%20brother%20because%20unfortunately%2C%20I%20didn't%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20meet%20him%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20action%20in%201999%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishal%20Batra%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20treat%20this%20place%20more%20as%20a%20pilgrimage.%20I%20came%20here%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202009.%20Since%20then%20I%20have%20been%20coming%20here%20every%20alternate%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20a%20twin%20sibling%2C%20I%20am%20blessed%20to%20keep%20telling%20his%20stories%20and%20carry%20forward%20his%20legacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishal%20Batra%20said%20it%20was%20a%20difficult%20moment%20when%20the%20news%20came.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20only%2024.%20I%20had%20never%20seen%20a%20dead%20body.%20I%20hate%20the%20word%20dead%20body.%20So%20when%20Vikram%20came%20in%20a%20coffin%2C%20we%20had%20to%20go%20to%20the%20command%20hospital%20in%20Palampur%20and%20identify%20the%20body.%20I%20had%20to%20sign%20the%20documents.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20sad%20moment%2C%20somebody%20asking%20you%20to%20recognise%20the%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishal%20Batra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20lift%20the%20body%20during%20the%20last%20rites.%20I%20believed%20that%20it%20would%20be%20my%20last%20touch%20of%20my%20brother%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishal%20Batra%20said%2C%20and%20choked%20up.%20%26quot%3BMy%20dad%20told%20me%20I%20have%20to%20lit%20the%20pyre.%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20courage.%20But%20I%20had%20to%20do%20it%20because%20if%20the%20father%20was%20not%20able%20to%2C%20the%20pandit%20ji%20told%20me%20I%20had%20to.%20Then%20I%20thought%20my%20brother%20deserves%20that%20last%20respect%20from%20my%20end.%20What%20he%20has%20done%2C%20I%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20match%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishal%20Batra%20said%2C%20looking%20at%20the%20first%20peak%20that%20Vishal%20Batra%20and%20the%20soldiers%20he%20led%20captured%2C%20'Point%205140'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20particular%20area%20in%20Kargil%20is%20now%20called%20Batra%20Top%20in%20honour%20of%20Captain%20Vikram%20Batra.%20%26quot%3BYeh%20dil%20mange%20more%26quot%3B%20was%20his%20victory%20warcry.%20The%202021%20Bollywood%20film%20'Shershah'%20was%20based%20on%20Captain%20Vikram%20Batra's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Point%205140%20was%20captured%2C%20the%2013%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Rifles%20was%20tasked%20to%20capture%20Point%204875.%20On%20July%207%2C%201999%20Captain%20Vikram%20Batra%20and%20his%20company%20were%20tasked%20to%20clear%20enemy%20defences%20from%20a%20narrow%20feature%20with%20sharp%20cuttings%20on%20both%20the%20sides%20leading%20up%20to%20Point%204875%20and%20a%20ledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20led%20the%20assault%20from%20the%20front%20and%20engaged%20the%20enemy%20in%20a%20physical%20fight.%20He%20killed%20five%20enemy%20soldiers%20at%20point%20blank%20range%20despite%20his%20own%20injuries.%20He%20moved%20towards%20the%20next%20enemy%20fortification%20and%20threw%20grenades%20to%20clear%20the%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20dauntless%20determination%20inspired%20his%20men%20to%20clear%20the%20enemy%20from%20a%20dominating%20position.%20Later%2C%20he%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries.%20His%20fearless%20determination%20and%20leadership%20encouraged%20his%20company%20men%20to%20avenge%20his%20death%20and%20finally%20capture%20Point%204875%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721904840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fobi6l0oo_vishal-batra_625x300_25_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fai-indians%2Fkargil-vijay-diwas-25th-anniversary-captain-vikram-batras-twin-chokes-up-looking-at-peak-his-brother-captured-6185985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vishal%20Batra%2