cretariat%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20because%20the%20Rashtrrapati%20Bhavan%20-%20the%20office%20and%20residence%20of%20the%20President%20of%20India%20-%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20continuous%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20make%20it%20more%20accessible%20to%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Durbar%20Hall%20is%20the%20venue%20of%20important%20ceremonies%20and%20celebrations%2C%20including%20the%20National%20Awards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20term%20'Durbar'%20refers%20to%20courts%20and%20assemblies%20of%20Indian%20rulers%20and%20the%20British.%20It%20lost%20relevance%20after%20India%20became%20a%20Republic%2C%20that%20is%2C%20'Ganatantra'.%20The%20concept%20of%20'Ganatantra'%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20Indian%20society%20since%20the%20ancient%20times%2C%20making%20'Ganatantra%20Mandap'%20an%20apt%20name%20for%20the%20venue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Hall%20was%20originally%20a%20ballroom%20and%20the%20Secretariat%20said%20the%20word%20'Ashok'%20connotes%20someone%20who%20is%20%26quot%3Bfree%20from%20all%20sufferings%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bbereft%20of%20any%20sorrow%26quot%3B%2C%20besides%20referring%20to%20Emperor%20Ashok%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20symbol%20of%20unity%20and%20peaceful%20co-existence%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRenaming%20'Ashok%20Hall'%20as%20'Ashok%20Mandap'%20brings%20uniformity%20in%20language%20and%20removes%20the%20traces%20of%20anglicisation%20while%20upholding%20the%20key%20values%20associated%20with%20the%20word%20'Ashok'%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20move%2C%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20government%20and%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20concept%20of%20'durbar'%20now%2C%20but%20the%20concept%20of%20'shahanshah'%20(emperor)%20still%20exists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn