uly%2031%2C%20where%20the%20talk%20will%20be%20dominated%20by%20the%20number%20of%20retentions%20teams%20can%20make%20and%20the%20Right%20to%20Match%20(RTM)%20options%20in%20hand%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202025%20mega%20auction.%20A%20report%20by%20Cricbuzz%20says%20IPL%20CEO%20Hemang%20Amin%20sent%20text%20messages%20to%20the%20franchise%20owners%20on%20Thursday%20morning%20for%20the%20meeting%20on%20July%2031%2C%20telling%20them%20that%20a%20formal%20invite%20with%20the%20venue%20and%20timing%20would%20follow.%20%E2%80%9CAmin%20is%20understood%20to%20have%20also%20indicated%20that%20the%20meeting%20would%20occur%20in%20the%20late%20afternoon%20or%20evening%20on%20July%2031.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20all%20the%20owners%20have%20confirmed%20their%20availability%20for%20the%20meeting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20exact%20venue%20has%20not%20been%20confirmed%2C%20the%20congregation%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20place%20at%20the%20Cricket%20Centre%2C%20the%20BCCI%20headquarters%2C%20located%20within%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20complex%20in%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20IPL%202018%20Mega%20Auction%2C%20franchises%20were%20allowed%20to%20retain%20up%20to%20five%20players%20-%20three%20from%20the%20auction%20-%20and%20others%20by%20using%20the%20Right%20to%20Match%20(RTM)%20card.%20But%20the%20introduction%20of%20two%20new%20teams%20-%20Gujarat%20Titans%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20-%20in%202022%20resulted%20in%20existing%20teams%20being%20allowed%20to%20retain%20four%20players%2C%20with%20no%20RTM%20card%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20the%20number%20of%20retentions%20could%20be%20kept%20at%20either%20five%20or%20six%20by%20BCCI.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20reasoning%20behind%20limiting%20retentions%20is%20that%20a%20higher%20number%20could%20diminish%20the%20excitement%20of%20the%20auction.%20If%20each%20team%20were%20to%20retain%20up%20to%20eight%20players%2C%20the%20top%2080%20players%20from%20around%20the%20world%20and%20India%20would%20be%20out%20of%20the%20auction%2C%20making%20the%20whole%20auction%20process%20a%20lacklustre%20affair.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Right%20To%20Match%20(RTM)%20option%20is%20a%20contentious%20issue%20that%20may%20be%20debated%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20although%20it's%20likely%20that%20the%20BCCI%20has%20already%20made%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721903700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdgdd4q2g_kkr-1_625x300_27_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmajor-changes-in-retentions-ahead-of-ipl-auction-report-makes-big-claim-6185712%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20meeting%20between%20the%20BCCI%20and%20all%20ten%20IPL%20franchise%20owners%20is%20all%20set%20to%20take%20place%20on%20July%2031%2C%20where%20the%20talk%20will%20be%20dominated%20by%20the%20number%20of%20retentions%20teams%20can%20make%20and%20the%20Right%20to%20Match%20(RTM)%20options.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmajor-changes-in-retentions-ahead-of-ipl-auction-report-makes-big-claim-6185712%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmajor-changes-in-retentions-ahead-of-ipl-auction-report-makes-big-claim-6185712%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmajor-changes-in-retentions-ahead-of-ipl-auction-report-makes-big-claim-6185712%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CD%20and%20Savings%20Rates%20Today%3A%20Supercharge%20Your%20Savings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcd-rates-savings-rates-today-thursd