%20'Ashok%20Mandap'%2C%20respectively%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Durbar%20Hall'%20is%20the%20venue%20of%20important%20ceremonies%20and%20celebrations%20such%20as%20the%20presentation%20of%20national%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20term%20'Durbar'%20refers%20to%20courts%20and%20assemblies%20of%20Indian%20rulers%20and%20the%20British.%20It%20lost%20relevance%20after%20India%20became%20a%20Republic%2C%20that%20is%2C%20'Ganatantra'.%20The%20concept%20of%20'Ganatantra'%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20Indian%20society%20since%20ancient%20times%2C%20making%20'Ganatantra%20Mandap'%20an%20apt%20name%20for%20the%20venue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Ashok%20Hall'%20was%20originally%20a%20ballroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20word%20'Ashok'%20connotes%20someone%20who%20is%20'free%20from%20all%20sufferings'%20or%20is%20'bereft%20of%20any%20sorrow'%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20'Ashoka'%20refers%20to%20Emperor%20Ashok%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20unity%20and%20peaceful%20co-existence%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20national%20emblem%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20India%20is%20the%20lion%20capital%20of%20Ashok%20from%20Sarnath.%20The%20word%20also%20refers%20to%20the%20Ashok%20tree%2C%20which%20has%20deep%20significance%20in%20Indian%20religious%20traditions%20as%20well%20as%20arts%20and%20culture.%20Renaming%20'Ashok%20Hall'%20as%20'Ashok%20Mandap'%20brings%20uniformity%20in%20language%20and%20removes%20the%20traces%20of%20anglicisation%20while%20upholding%20the%20key%20values%20associated%20with%20the%20word%20'Ashok'%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721900160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Fh7ru9m08_rashtrapati-bhavan_650x400_09