l-deadpool-wolverine-be-available-for-digital-streaming%2Farticleshow%2F112012982.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What%20Is%20'Project%2025'%2C%20A%20Document%20Trump%20Has%20'Distanced'%20Himself%20From%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fijic88h_project-2025_625x300_25_July_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20greatest%20electoral%20races%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20election%20to%20the%20office%20of%20the%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%20(POTUS)%2C%20is%20about%20to%20begin.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20fourth%20week%20of%20August%2C%20Democrats%20will%20finalise%20their%20candidate%20to%20take%20on%20former%20President%20and%20Republican%20nominee%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20disastrous%20debate%20last%20month%20between%20Biden%20and%20Trump%2C%20Democrats%20are%20now%20struggling%20with%20the%20candidature%20of%20the%20incumbent%20POTUS%20after%20he%20recently%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20not%20seek%20re-election.%20His%20endorsement%20of%20Vice-President%20Kamala%20Harris%20has%20yet%20to%20secure%20final%20approval%20from%20party%20leaders.%20Naturally%2C%20time%20is%20short%20for%20the%20Democrats%20to%20mount%20an%20effective%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20political%20landscape%20changed%20drastically%20after%20Trump%20escaped%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Though%20many%20argue%20that%20the%20election%20is%20not%20a%20done%20deal%20yet%2C%20the%20odds%20seem%20to%20favour%20the%20GOP%20heavily%20as%20of%20now.%20The%20party%20may%20wrest%20not%20only%20the%20White%20House%20but%20both%20Houses%20of%20the%20U.S.%20Congress%2C%20that%20is%2C%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20and%20the%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Transition%20Project'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernments%20and%20administrations%20across%20the%20globe%20are%20trying%20to%20estimate%20what%20a%20second%20Trump%20administration%20might%20bring.%20Of%20course%2C%20unlike%202016%2C%20they%20now%20have%20the%20benefit%20of%20hindsight%20to%20draft%20a%20calibrated%20policy%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20United%20States.%20Here%2C%20besides%20previous%20experience%2C%20policy%20planners%20are%20dipping%20into%20a%20900-odd%20page%20document%2C%20the%202025%20Presidential%20Transition%20Project%2C%20in%20which%20domain%20experts%20have%20listed%20department-wise%20policy%20prescriptions%20and%20drawn%20a%20roadmap%20for%20the%20Conservatives%20to%20effect%20fundamental%20changes%20in%20the%20way%20the%20country%20is%20governed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Project%2C%20helmed%20by%20Heritage%20Foundation%2C%20a%20Washington-based%20think%20tank%20that%20reflects%20Republican%20views%2C%20is%20considered%20a%20key%20and%20expansive%20input%20given%20that%20Trump%20in%20his%20first%20administration%20had%20drawn%20heavily%20from%20the%20organisation's%20expertise.%20Trump%20may%20not%20have%20officially%20granted%20recognition%20to%20the%20document%2C%20but%20it%20is%20being%20read%20by%20policy%20planners%20with%20wide%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20India-US%20Relations%20May%20Evolve%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilateral%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20democracies%20are%20characterised%20by%20India%20as%20a%20'Comprehensive%20Global%20Strategic%20Partnership'.%20One%20defining%20feature%20of%20that%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20New%20Delhi%20enjoys%20bipartisan%20support%20in%20Washington.%20Successive%20administrations%2C%20whether%20Democrat%20or%20Republican%2C%20have%20continued%20to%20engage%20with%20India.%20From%20deep%20sea%20to%20outer%20space%2C%20the%20partnership%20encompasses%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20subjects.%20By%20extension%2C%20members%20of%20the%20U.S.%20Congress%20have%20also%20shown%20a%20greater%20accommodative%20spirit%20over%20the%20last%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20multi-sector%20engagement%2C%20three%20key%20areas%20have%20been%20defence%20cooperation%2C%20strategic%20engagement%20and%20trade%20and%20investment.%20Going%20by%20his%20previous%20administration%2C%20these%20are%20likely%20to%20remain%20Trump's%20top%20priorities%20if%20he%20manages%20to%20return%20as%20President.%20He%20is%20riding%20on%20his%20'Make%20America%20Great%20Again'%20pitch%20and%20aims%20to%20restore%20to%20the%20US%20shop%20floors%20across%20industrial%20units%20that%20shifted%20their%20jobs%20to%20off-shore%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20In%20For%20Trade%20Relations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatistics%20for%202022%20show%20that%20the%20India-US%20bilateral%20trade%20for%20merchandise%20and%20services%20stood%20at%20%24191.43%20billion.%20Of%20this%2C%20while%20India's%20exports%20accounted%20for%20%24118.53%20billion%2C%20US%20exports%20were%20around%20%2472.90%20billion.%20India%20enjoyed%20a%20balance%20of%20trade%20of%20over%20%24100%20billion%20in%20its%20favour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20Trump%20administration%20is%20expected%20to%20exert%20pressure%20towards%20expanding%20trade%20and%20services%20with%20all%20countries%2C%20including%20India.%20The%20section%20on%20trade%20in%20the%20Project%202025%20report%2C%20quoting%20US%20government%20figures%2C%20states%20that%20of%20the%20%241%2C138%20billion%20deficit%20that%20the%20US%20has%20with%2014%20major%20trading%20partners%2C%20India%20is%20in%2011th%20position.%20Negotiators%20can%20expect%20hard%20bargaining%2C%20with%20each%20side%20insisting%20on%20securing%20the%20best%20deal%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefence%20And%20Strategic%20Ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20in%20this%20sector%20continue%20to%20flourish%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Framework%20for%20Defence%20Cooperation%20in%202005%2C%20which%20was%20renewed%20for%20another%20decade%20in%202015.%20Besides%20designating%20India%20as%20a%20'Major%20Defence%20Partner'%2C%20the%20pact%20moved%20up%20New%20Delhi%20to%20grant%20it%20licence%20exemption%20for%20Strategic%20Trade%20Authorisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20both%20sides%20also%20finalised%20a%20Defence%20Industrial%20Cooperation%20Roadmap%20and%20launched%20a%20Defence%20Acceleration%20Ecosystem%20to%20build%20a%20network%20of%20universities%2C%20incubators%2C%20think%20tanks%20and%20private%20investments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sector%20will%20be%20watched%20with%20much%20interest%20given%20that%20India%20is%20working%20on%20a%20plan%20to%20build%20specialised%20industrial%20corridors%20to%20manufacture%20defence%20equipment%20in%20the%20country%20with%20technology%20transfers%2C%20something%20that%20American%20companies%20working%20with%20critical%20technologies%20are%20not%20particularly%20keen%20about.%20However%2C%20this%20contrasts%20with%20the%20decision%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20to%20provide%20India%20with%20incentives%20to%20wean%20it%20away%20from%20Russian%20military%20hardware.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20India%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Quad%20and%20Indo-Pacific%20groupings%2C%20both%20of%20which%20got%20a%20boost%20during%20the%20previous%20Trump%20administration.%20While%20China%2C%20Iran%20and%20North%20Korea%20occupy%20a%20central%20place%20in%20the%20report's%20analysis%2C%20India's%20reference%20in%20the%20document%20appears%20in%20relation%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20tensions%20over%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20suggests%20a%20'Quad%20Plus'%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong