nifer-aniston-fires-back-at-jd-vances-childless-cat-ladies-remark-targeting-us-vp-kamala-harris%2Farticleshow%2F112008115.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjennifer-aniston-fires-back-at-jd-vances-childless-cat-ladies-remark-targeting-us-vp-kamala-harris%2Famp_articleshow%2F112008115.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjennifer-aniston-fires-back-at-jd-vances-childless-cat-ladies-remark-targeting-us-vp-kamala-harris%2Famp_articleshow%2F112008115.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Failed%20at%20UPSC%2C%20Not%20in%20Life%3A%20%E2%80%98How%20I%20Battled%20Depression%20to%20Rebuild%20Life%20After%206%20Failed%20Attempts%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wee%20hours%20of%2024%20October%202020%2C%20Kajal%20Srivastava%20was%20standing%20on%20the%20balcony%20of%20her%20home%20in%20Greater%20Noida.%20Staring%20down%20from%20the%20eighth%20floor%20of%20her%20apartment%2C%20she%20yearned%20to%20jump%20off%20the%20balcony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20for%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20examinations%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347611%2Fupsc-cse-2023-final-list-toppers-ias-officer-jitin-yadav-viral-tweet-on-failure-aspirants-inspiration%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20%3C%2Fa%3E(CSE)%20%E2%80%93%20were%20out%20and%20she%20did%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20list%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20become%20an%20IPS%20officer.%20I%20was%20so%20sure%20of%20my%20success%20but%20I%20failed%20to%20clear%20UPSC%20even%20in%20my%20last%20chance.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20dare%20to%20tell%20anyone%20about%20the%20result.%20I%20wanted%20to%20jump%20off%20the%20balcony%20not%20because%20I%20had%20failed%20again%20but%20because%20I%20was%20tired.%20I%20was%20too%20tired%20to%20prove%20myself.%20I%20was%20too%20tired%20to%20give%20myself%20more%20chances.%20I%20wanted%20peace%20instantly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20in%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20sister%20found%20her%20in%20this%20vulnerable%20state%20and%20hugged%20her%20tightly%20as%20she%20sobbed%20in%20her%20arms.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20told%20me%20that%20I%20was%20not%20a%20failure%20and%20if%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20serve%20the%20country%20by%20becoming%20an%20IPS%20officer%2C%20then%20another%20big%20opportunity%20was%20waiting%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kajal%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20day%2C%20Kajal%20mustered%20the%20strength%20and%20sat%20down%20at%20her%20study%20table.%20On%20a%20blank%20sheet%20of%20paper%2C%20she%20wrote%20%E2%80%9CTAVASI%20%E2%80%93%20my%20movement%20of%20courage%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-1-1721879477.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kajal%20Srivastava%20was%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20giving%20up%20on%20life%20after%20six%20failed%20UPSC%20CSE%20attempts.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-1-1721879477.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-1-1721879477-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-1-1721879477-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-1-1721879477-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-1-1721879477-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358418%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKajal%20Srivastava%20was%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20giving%20up%20on%20life%20after%20six%20failed%20UPSC%20CSE%20attempts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20six-year-long%20hustle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20from%20Hansraj%20College%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Kajal%20took%20admission%20in%20a%20prestigious%20coaching%20institute%20in%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20to%20prepare%20for%20UPSC%20CSE.%20Her%20day%20started%20with%20attending%20coaching%20classes%20from%208%20to%2011%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20come%20to%20my%20room%2C%20which%20was%20more%20like%20a%20hole.%20It%20had%20a%20small%20bed%20with%20termites%20and%20bed%20bugs%2C%20a%20small%20chair%2C%20a%20table%2C%20and%20an%20almirah.%20There%20was%20a%20small%20exhaust%20fan%20which%20was%20the%20only%20source%20of%20natural%20light%20and%20ventilation.%20Anybody%20could%20become%20claustrophobic%20in%20that%20room%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20was%20paying%20Rs%2014%2C000%20for%20that%20tiny%20room.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20ask%20for%20more%20money%20from%20my%20parents.%20I%20had%20already%20spent%20Rs%202%20lakh%20on%20coaching%20fees.%20The%20first%20step%20for%20me%20was%20to%20survive%20in%20this%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAway%20from%20the%20comforts%20of%20her%20home%2C%20Kajal%20dedicated%20herself%20to%20preparation.%20In%202014%2C%20she%20gave%20her%20first%20attempt%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20the%20preliminary%20stage.%20She%20reappeared%20for%20the%20exam%20in%202015%20but%20failed%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20then%2C%20everybody%20started%20telling%20my%20parents%20that%20I%20was%20wasting%20their%20time%20and%20money.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20was%20surviving%20on%20a%20bare%20minimum%20lifestyle%2C%20sometimes%20skipping%20meals.%20If%20I%20met%20a%20friend%20or%20