0them%2C%20effectively%20reusing%20the%20water.%20In%20summer%20months%2C%20we%20also%20use%20it%20to%20water%20the%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deshmukh.%20Even%20if%20we%20consider%20that%20it%20takes%20about%2010%20litres%20of%20water%20to%20wash%20a%20car%20and%20five%20litres%20to%20wash%20a%20two-wheeler%2C%20this%20system%20saves%20over%2019%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20month!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20society%20members%20are%20now%20exploring%20ways%20to%20become%20completely%20self-sufficient%20for%20their%20water%20needs.%20Shaligram%20mentions%20that%20they%20are%20happy%20to%20guide%20other%20societies%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354201%2Fhow-to-set-up-start-rainwater-harvesting-affordable-system-diy-steps-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimplementing%20similar%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%20and%20the%20AC%20condensate%20pipes%20each%20currently%20cost%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20install.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWater%20is%20a%20finite%20resource.%20We%20need%20to%20save%20it%20in%20whatever%20way%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsmaller-toilet-tanks-could-save-10-of-water%2Farticleshow%2F46843707.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Smaller%20toilet%20tanks%20could%20save%2010%20%25%20of%20water%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20Published%20On%208%20April%2C%202015%20Courtesy%20Times%20Of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fmumbai-to-face-5-water-cut-from-may-30-10-from-june-5-as-lake-levels-fall-430938-2024-05-26%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Mumbai%20to%20fac